A colossal, intricately detailed Eldrazi Drone, El Drazi, dominates a desolate, rocky wasteland under a bruised purple sky. Its metallic body is scarred and weathered, with glowing crimson optics and multiple missile launchers firing bursts of energy. In the foreground, a terrified humanoid figure is dodging laser fire, caught in two shots. Dramatic lighting, cinematic, epic fantasy, intricate detail, hyperrealistic.